            <p style="color: #3273dc; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; background-color: #eff5fb; padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem; display: inline-block; border-radius: 4px;">env_02 <span lang="zh">（较新的环境）</span><span lang="en">(Newer Environment)</span></p>
